race.comment: Open race to close out the card. BLITZUM (1) has a handy record over this six-furlong journey with a win and three placings from six attempts and will be ready to peak now third-up from the break. Gets 3kg off from the low draw and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. CEEKAY'S CHOICE (11) is a consistent conveyance who is yet to miss the top-five in nine career outings. Yet to put in a poor one and has to be included. EXTREME SPIRIT (5) doesn't win out of turn but is usually around the money and can trouble the judge with any luck in running. LANTAU ISLAND (4) gets the Gollan/Maloney combination and can make his presence felt third-up from the spell. WARILLA GORILLA (7) next best from the inside alley.
